==Demographics==

The racial makeup of the Hernandez ZCTA was 58.4% [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|White]], 0.4% [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|African American]], 2.6% [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|Native American]], 0.4% [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|Asian]], 35.3% from [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|other races]], and 2.9% from two or more races.<ref name="2010 Characteristics">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov |title=Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics: 2010 ZCTA5 87637 - Hernandez NM |publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]] |access-date=November 2, 2017}}</ref> [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|Hispanic]] or [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|Latino]] of any race were 88.9% of the population.<ref name="2010 Characteristics"/>

